{"tid":1459112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FC的重要性","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:08:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:22:32.000Z","uid":293050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5d93930f13fe80322be3f9331d440df9ebe3a8","tid":1459112,"uid":293050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"今日發夢係機場 4點尾近5點不斷有人呼叫要走 會清場<br />\n更有好心人寫住大字報話俾大家知唔放催淚彈但會用布袋彈等等 <br />\n我身旁友人係HX員工 就上前求證<br />\n好心人就話「FACT CHECKED HX叫員工唔洗返工 6點封機場 但用布袋彈同橡膠子彈係傳聞」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J9ZqnF3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ9ZqnF3.jpg&h=c6d85bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想表達嘅係 &lsquo;FACT CHECKED&rsquo;真係好重要<br />\n當時我附近真係好多人因為咁而散得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真心 我係好appreciate有人去做哨兵 <br />\n但只係想大家 真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">FACT CHECKED</span>先好放出黎 傳聞嘅野等一等 大家一齊努力求證左先放出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家今日真係好齊心 贏左好靚仔嘅一仗<br />\n尋晚咁倉卒都一呼百應到一齊塞爆機場 好感動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n塞機場係岩架 繼續啦兄弟！<br />\n每日一點鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSORRY P牌仔唔識出PO 1999<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割席 點樣都不割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34651641a9e864512229d0ab4871a86c728e1cec","tid":1459112,"uid":293050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"只推十連"},{"pid":"836afddfee565b1549ea7364acd5d081cb01f74f","tid":1459112,"uid":293050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:09:33.000Z","msg":"自推十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6dceecedb3af87c9baa1a2253168ce38128dce","tid":1459112,"uid":293050,"like":0,"disli